    "Federated learning enables a unified machine learning model to be trained from local data of multiple participants while protecting data privacy.",
    "Figure 1 illustrates the Federated Learning Algorithm Model.",
    "Federated transfer learning is a data distribution situation in which horizontal federated learning and vertical federated learning do not match.There are also two methods of privacy protection [4] in the federal learning mode: encryption and disturbance.",
    "However, federated learning is currently in the infancy of research and still faces many problems in both technology and deployment.",
    "Homomorphic Encryption (HE)Homomorphic encryption (HE) is a cryptographic technique that allows for computations to be performed on ciphertext without the need for decryption."
